org.jetel.graph.runtime.tracker

Class ReformatComponentTokenTracker

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jetel.graph.runtime.tracker.BasicComponentTokenTracker
      • org.jetel.graph.runtime.tracker.ComplexComponentTokenTracker
        • org.jetel.graph.runtime.tracker.ReformatComponentTokenTracker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ComponentTokenTracker
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FileOperationComponentTokenTracker

    public class ReformatComponentTokenTracker
extends ComplexComponentTokenTracker
    Token tracker for components creating N out-tokens for each in-token. The 1st of the N tokens is unified with the last read input token (which is the only difference between this and ComplexComponentTokenTracker), all other N-1 out-tokens are linked to the last read token.
